+| Home Miner Daemon | `services/home-miner-daemon/daemon.py` | Complete |
+| Store (Principal + Pairing) | `services/home-miner-daemon/store.py` | Complete |
+| Event Spine | `services/home-miner-daemon/spine.py` | Complete |
